{"tid":2162754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年涉6.12金鐘襲警續審 辯方指被告因拍攝警暴被捉","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T10:35:42.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"297a2de87e7427e1809d105cb2dd7c9c698db157","tid":2162754,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"警長方樂文早前作供形容被告大力推他，他感到痛楚，一兩小時後查看胸口仍見紅印，不過當時忙著返回崗位「止暴制亂」，沒有拍下傷勢，亦未覺嚴重到需要求醫。<br />\n<br />\n她受盤問時表示，不知道方衝出防線的原因，亦不知方為何突然後退。她同意自己看不到被告推方胸口，方亦沒向她展示傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n辯方向女警長播出三段事發前後的影片，影片可見當時有其他人被警方截查或拘捕，然後見到速龍小隊警員著在場人士「退後啲」，繼而聽到有人說<span class=\"red\">「認住嗰個戴眼鏡著黑衫」、「喂！留意戴手套嗰幾個，有機會捉佢過嚟」</span>，隨即警員衝出防線捉人，眾人爭相逃跑，其後有女聲哭訴男友被捕，並稱「見到戴手套就要拉」，亦有人大叫：「救命呀！打人呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/2VZTFUOHCNHMXMIE2P6NV5F2TQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F2VZTFUOHCNHMXMIE2P6NV5F2TQ%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=947017de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F2VZTFUOHCNHMXMIE2P6NV5F2TQ%2F&h=54ae0c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/2VZTFUOHCNHMXMIE2P6NV5F2TQ/</a>"},{"pid":"337177c46ddac26c7f58c2d715b1abe13539bc3b","tid":2162754,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73366f26aff960ed7ad526dd08d638276872adb2","tid":2162754,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149f2a3d7e10b8dfbe17f36b264c